Invocation Name: rangers cup counter
des:
Tell you how many days ago the New York Rangers won their last Stanley cup.

Let's all hope one day it will tell us "zero days ago".

This skill is unofficial and not affiliated with the New York Rangers team or the The National Hockey League.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
